stats.passive1: Point Runner: Builds up to 20% bonus movement speed over 2 seconds while near turrets, fallen turrets and Void Gates.
stats.passive2: Favor: Nearby enemy minions, killed by any ally other than you, will sometimes drop a coin that can be picked up to either grant 50 or restore 6% missing mana (minimum 10). Gold coin can only drop if an allied champion is nearby. Cannon minions will drop a coin as long as you don't kill them.
stats.passive3: Quest: Earn 750 using this item. Reward: Favor is upgraded to Emperor's Favor making champion takedowns grant both the gold and mana. You also grant 8% bonus movement speed to nearby allied champions moving toward you.
stats.active: Unique: Grants nearby allies +40% bonus movement speed for 3 seconds (60 second cooldown).

other.limit: Limited to 1 Jungle or Gold Income item.
